algorithms.maze3DGenerators

Class Maze3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.maze3DGenerators.Maze3D

  • public class Maze3D
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class Maze3d defines the representation of three-dimensional maze Hold zAxis, xAxis, yAxis dimensions
    zAxis - represent the floors
    xAxis - represent the rows
    yAxis - represent the columns
    The 3D maze represent by three dimensional array of integer: int[zAxis][xAxis][yAxis]
    Since:
    2016-30-07
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Asi Belachow
